The flight was smooth, except above a wide lake where it was rainy.
AzureBlade had to transform to jet mode in order to get past it more
easily. He managed to arrive in the vincinity of the Predacon base and
to send a message.

AzureBlade: Predacons, my name is AzureBlade, Protoform Z. I come here
to discuss war matters with you.
